/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a high vantage point, providing a bird's eye view of the urban landscape. The street, teeming with life, stretches out below, flanked by buildings on one side and verdant trees on the other. Cars and buses, symbols of the city's constant motion, are scattered along the road, adding to the dynamic nature of the scene. The sky overhead is a blanket of overcast clouds, casting a soft, diffused light over the cityscape. The predominant colors in the image are shades of green from the trees and gray from the buildings and roads, creating a harmonious blend that is characteristic of urban landscapes.
